id: pm-gvk2
title: Extract reusable semantic HTTP mock fixtures
description: "Duplicate audit 2026-05-22: semantic/vector tests duplicate globalThis.fetch stubs for OpenAI embeddings and Qdrant upsert responses. The repeated mock block appears in tests/unit/health-command.spec.ts:539, tests/unit/reindex-command.spec.ts:204, and tests/unit/search-cache.spec.ts, including the same /v1/embeddings and /collections/pm_items/points?wait=true response handling. This is separate from the broader shared item factory duplication because it is domain-specific semantic infrastructure with enough behavior to drift. Fix by adding a focused helper such as installSemanticFetchMock({ embeddings, qdrantStatus, captureCalls }) and migrating health/reindex/search-cache tests to it."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: dedup,search,tests
