acceptance_criteria: "Semantic tests share one typed HTTP mock fixture for embeddings and Qdrant responses; tests can still customize input-count embeddings and failure paths; duplicated global fetch setup/restore blocks are removed from health, reindex, and search-cache specs; targeted semantic/search tests pass."
